PN,40101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778061972
OL,3,COpera singer who hid deafness for 30
OL,4,Cyears describes 'life-changing' surgery
OL,6,FAn opera singer who hid her deafness
OL,7,Ffor over 30 years has described "life-
OL,8,Fchanging" surgery that has the
OL,9,Fpotential to become the norm for
OL,10,Fthousands of NHS patients.
OL,12,FJanine Roebuck, 72, from London, had
OL,13,Fdouble cochlear implants fitted to
OL,14,Frestore her hearing, a method now
OL,15,Fbeing trialled nationwide to see
OL,16,Fwhether it can transform the lives of
OL,17,Fthousands more people.
OL,26,@oD@aOUpD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
