OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778061972
OL,3,COpera singer who hid deafness for 30
OL,4,Cyears describes 'life-changing' surgery
OL,6,FUnder current guidelines from the
OL,7,FNational Institute for Health and Care
OL,8,FExcellence (Nice), the vast majority
OL,9,Fof deaf adults are only eligible for
OL,10,Fone cochlear implant.
OL,12,FThis is based on analysis suggesting
OL,13,Fthat offering two is not cost
OL,14,Feffective for the NHS and a lack of
OL,15,Fevidence in the area.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778061972
OL,3,COpera singer who hid deafness for 30
OL,4,Cyears describes 'life-changing' surgery
OL,6,FTo address this, the National
OL,7,FInstitute for Health and Care Research
OL,8,F(NIHR), which receives Government
OL,9,Ffunding, is backing a new study into
OL,10,Ftwo implants for adults, which is
OL,11,Fbeing led by Addenbrooke's Hospital
OL,12,Fand the University of Cambridge.
OL,14,FMs Roebuck suffers from the inherited
OL,15,Fcondition sensorineural hearing loss,
OL,16,Fwhich accounts for around 70% of all
OL,17,Fcases of genetic hearing loss.
OL,19,FThe condition has been carried down
OL,20,Fthrough generations of her family.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778061972
OL,3,COpera singer who hid deafness for 30
OL,4,Cyears describes 'life-changing' surgery
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIn 2019, she underwent cochlear
OL,12,Fimplant surgery on the NHS for one
OL,13,Fear, as per the guidelines, but
OL,14,Fdecided to pay to have the other ear
OL,15,Fdone at the same time using her own
OL,16,Fmoney.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778061972
OL,3,COpera singer who hid deafness for 30
OL,4,Cyears describes 'life-changing' surgery
OL,6,FFor more than 30 years, she had hid
OL,7,Fher deteriorating hearing, despite
OL,8,Fbeing a mezzo-soprano, performing in
OL,9,Foperas, operettas and musicals,
OL,10,Fincluding at the Royal Opera House in
OL,11,FLondon. She has now retired.
OL,13,FShe said having the surgery was "the
OL,14,Fbest thing I've ever done in my life",
OL,15,Fadding: "Having two implants is light
OL,16,Fyears away from just one.
OL,18,F"Sound quality is so much better,
OL,19,Fsounds are fuller, clearer, louder and
OL,20,Fmore natural.
OL,26,@uD@aOUvD@eO]wD@IOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778061972
OL,3,COpera singer who hid deafness for 30
OL,4,Cyears describes 'life-changing' surgery
OL,6,F"It's much easier to tell where sounds
OL,7,Fare coming from, especially in busy
OL,8,Fspaces.
OL,10,F"If you're out in public, it can be
OL,11,Fhard to follow who is speaking, making
OL,12,Fjoining in with conversations almost
OL,13,Fimpossible.
OL,15,F"As a result, you have debilitating
OL,16,Fconcentration fatigue at the end of
OL,17,Fevery day."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778061972
OL,3,COpera singer who hid deafness for 30
OL,4,Cyears describes 'life-changing' surgery
OL,6,FShe described how the surgery has
OL,7,Fdramatically improved her life,
OL,8,Fadding: "With bilateral implants, I no
OL,9,Flonger consider myself to be deaf.
OL,11,F"They have been utterly life-changing
OL,12,Fand, for me, have broken a
OL,13,Fgenerational curse.
OL,15,F"Struggling to hear can be extremely
OL,16,Fisolating and many people experience
OL,17,Fanxiety or depression as a result.
OL,19,F"The implants are life-changing. They
OL,20,Freconnect you to the world and, most
OL,21,Fimportantly, people.
OL,26,@pD@IOUsD@AOUwD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778061972
OL,3,COpera singer who hid deafness for 30
OL,4,Cyears describes 'life-changing' surgery
OL,6,F"Communication is surely the longing
OL,7,Fof every human heart.
OL,9,F"I also feel safer and more secure
OL,10,Fhaving the two implants.
OL,12,F"I am more aware of and connected to
OL,13,Fwhat's happening in the world around
OL,14,Fme.
OL,16,F"And, if anything goes wrong with one
OL,17,Fof the implants, I'm not suddenly
OL,18,Fplunged into a world of total silence."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUtD@AOUxD@AOUzD@gO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778061972
OL,3,COpera singer who hid deafness for 30
OL,4,Cyears describes 'life-changing' surgery
OL,6,FShe told the Press Association her
OL,7,Ffather had the same condition and
OL,8,F"dealt with it graciously and
OL,9,Fbravely". Her grandfather and his
OL,10,Fbrothers and sisters struggled too.
OL,12,FShe said having the implants switched
OL,13,Fon gave her joy and over the next six
OL,14,Fmonths she discovered new sounds.
OL,16,FShe said: "The one that actually made
OL,17,Fme weep was, I was in the kitchen and
OL,18,FI could hear this noise, and it wasn't
OL,19,Fthe tap, it wasn't the cooker, it
OL,20,Fwasn't the oven, and I'm thinking, 'oh
OL,21,Fmy god, what is it?'
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@HO]xD@KOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778061972
OL,3,COpera singer who hid deafness for 30
OL,4,Cyears describes 'life-changing' surgery
OL,6,F"And the door into the garden was
OL,7,Fopen, and it was pouring with rain,
OL,8,Fand it was the sound of rain on the
OL,9,Fleaves. I didn't even know that was a
OL,10,Fsound."
OL,12,FThe new trial will run in 14 hospitals
OL,13,Fand includes more than 250 adults.
OL,15,FThey will receive either one
OL,16,F(unilateral) or two (bilateral)
OL,17,Fimplants so results can be compared.
OL,19,FThose in the trial will need to have
OL,20,Fbecome deaf later in life and cannot
OL,21,Falready have an implant.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778061972
OL,3,COpera singer who hid deafness for 30
OL,4,Cyears describes 'life-changing' surgery
OL,6,FMatthew Smith, an ear, nose and throat
OL,7,F(ENT) surgeon at Addenbrooke's
OL,8,FHospital, and Professor Debi Vickers,
OL,9,Fa speech and hearing scientist in the
OL,10,Fdepartment of clinical neurosciences,
OL,11,FUniversity of Cambridge, are leading
OL,12,Fthe study.
OL,14,FMr Smith said: "We know from giving
OL,15,Fbilateral implants to children that it
OL,16,Fcan have a transformative effect on
OL,17,Ftheir quality of life and interactions
OL,18,Fwith other people.
OL,26,@vD@POU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778061972
OL,3,COpera singer who hid deafness for 30
OL,4,Cyears describes 'life-changing' surgery
OL,6,F"Through this study, we can offer the
OL,7,Fsame opportunity to adults who have
OL,8,Fbecome deaf, and understand the
OL,9,Fpotential added value of bilateral
OL,10,Fcochlear implants, not just in terms
OL,11,Fof hearing, but also how they enrich
OL,12,Fquality of life."
OL,14,FProf Vickers said: "Children routinely
OL,15,Freceive bilateral cochlear implants.
OL,17,F"These can provide three-dimensional
OL,18,Fhearing, enabling them to hear more
OL,19,Fnaturally than unilateral, with
OL,20,Fimproved access to sound and better
OL,21,Fengagement with society.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@QO]vD@TOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G12/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778061972
OL,3,COpera singer who hid deafness for 30
OL,4,Cyears describes 'life-changing' surgery
OL,6,F"Adults tell us, and I agree, that
OL,7,Fthey should be given the same hearing
OL,8,Fopportunities as children.
OL,10,F"In turn, these will result in reduced
OL,11,Fsocial isolation, enriched
OL,12,Fcommunication, improved mental health,
OL,13,Fand better overall quality of life".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G13/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778061972
OL,3,COpera singer who hid deafness for 30
OL,4,Cyears describes 'life-changing' surgery
OL,6,FProfessor Anthony Gordon, programme
OL,7,Fdirector for the NIHR health
OL,8,Ftechnology assessment programme, which
OL,9,Ffunded the trial, said: "This study
OL,10,Foffers real hope to people with severe
OL,11,Fhearing loss and the chance of a
OL,12,Fsignificant improvement in their
OL,13,Fquality of life."
OL,15,FOnce the trial finishes, it will be
OL,16,Fsubmitted to Nice who can review it.
OL,26,@qD@YOUuD@QO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G14/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778061972
OL,3,COpera singer who hid deafness for 30
OL,4,Cyears describes 'life-changing' surgery
OL,6,FRalph Holme, director of research at
OL,7,Fthe RNID, said: "It's wonderful to
OL,8,Fhear just how lifechanging this
OL,9,Fexperience has been for Janine, and
OL,10,Fthe impact it's had on her quality of
OL,11,Flife.
OL,13,F"Cochlear implants can be truly
OL,14,Ftransformative for people with hearing
OL,15,Floss, helping them reconnect with the
OL,16,Fworld around them, and with friends,
OL,17,Ffamily and colleagues.
OL,26,@oD@QOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G15/16
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778061972
OL,3,COpera singer who hid deafness for 30
OL,4,Cyears describes 'life-changing' surgery
OL,6,F"The added benefits bilateral implants
OL,7,Fcould bring are particularly exciting,
OL,8,Fand this study will play a vital role
OL,9,Fin building the evidence needed so
OL,10,Fthat many more people can benefit,
OL,11,Fjust as Janine has.
OL,13,F"Hearing loss and tinnitus affect 18
OL,14,Fmillion people in the UK, and trials
OL,15,Flike this offer genuine hope for a
OL,16,Ffuture in which effective treatments
OL,17,Fare available to everyone who wants
OL,18,Fthem."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G16/16
